{"parentUuid":"536d3148-a82b-4bff-ba66-c71c0a4b73c4","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GAsiyQmZrBK4L6BmvCdzVC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**\"Bloviating…\"** means Claude is actively generating a response (not connecting — that would show a different status like \"Connecting…\").\n\n**Common causes for 3+ minute delays:**\n\n1. **Large tool output being processed** — if a previous tool call returned a huge amount of data (e.g., a massive grep result, long file read), Claude has to process all of it before responding\n2. **Complex reasoning** — extended thinking on a difficult problem\n3. **Slow streaming** — network hiccup causing the token stream to stall mid-response\n4. **Context window near limit** — processing gets slower as context fills up; the system will auto-compress but that takes time\n\n**What you can do:**\n\n- Press `Escape` to interrupt and see what's happened so far\n- If it's truly stuck (no new tokens), `Ctrl+C` to kill and retry with a simpler/scoped request\n- Check if a previous tool call returned an unusually large result that might be causing it to spin\n\nThe spinner text (\"Bloviating\", \"Thinking\", \"Pondering\", etc.) in Claude Code is just flavor text — they all mean the same thing: model is generating."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29936,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":381,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":29936,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZCfrmckPgdgggDWX5p1L","type":"assistant","uuid":"dc375fcd-2f9a-4c93-b5fb-edd57ff6ed19","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:24:58.370Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/shunkakinoki/dotfiles","sessionId":"d8f66867-5fea-4faa-814f-b67f714fad74"